{"tid":818652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「撐警大聯盟」在得悉朱上訴失敗庭外高叫 「林鄭月娥下台」","createTime":"2018-09-14T08:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T11:10:09.000Z","uid":55981,"like":173,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"0b7c3f5ba30ce9f18602e3741d31b43168b189ff","tid":818652,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180914/large/1536914181_3efd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180914%2Flarge%2F1536914181_3efd.jpg&h=51b6bbcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十數名支持朱經緯的「撐警大聯盟」市民，在得悉朱上訴失敗，要重返獄中過中秋後，在庭外高叫「法治已死，香港沉淪」、「特首無能，香港已死」、「警察抗暴，被拉被鎖」、「林鄭月娥下台」等口號，而愛港之聲、珍惜群組等團體同時在執拾物品離開。<br />\n<br />\n今午有近百名支持者到庭撐朱經緯，坐滿整個法庭延伸大堂，曾替朱撰寫求情信的退休警務處刑事及保安處處長羅夢熊、朱的前妻均有到庭聽取判決。坐在法庭延伸部分的支持者聞判一臉愕然，部分人直至散庭後始從記者口中得知判決，即低聲說「仆街」。有數名支持者落淚，不斷用紙巾拭淚。<br />\n<br />\n記者鄭語霆 蘇曉欣"},{"pid":"4a092e5485c68bc7cd160f7b39e999ec644392db","tid":818652,"uid":14918,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:59:21.000Z","msg":"反了 反了<br />\n<br />\n究竟幫朱蛇定害佢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc18241db21d0f8ebb38ab0d258412c7c65f522","tid":818652,"uid":23376,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:02:32.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72549137e26e1ebb151723fff45fa91f54382c0d","tid":818652,"uid":62247,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而愛港之聲、珍惜群組等團體同時在執拾物品離開。</blockquote><br />\n收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走住屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a5263794d22188362c61220457d038566986da","tid":818652,"uid":208159,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018